v 2.0
"Looking Glass" - To add a "looking glass" type of feature, that will allow admins. to run a pre-defined set of commands
directly from a SRX and display the output in the GUI

"Refresh" - To allow the admin to get new messages from the kmd-logs file without the need to exit/reopen the application

"Installer" - To create an installer for both Windows and MacOS

v 3.0
"Compare configurations" - To add a feature that will allow an administrator to extract the VPN configuration for 2x SRXs
and compare the differences
